<br>
It took me a couple of nights (few hours each night) to get the heart of fire to drop. Yes, I got it from an inferno wiz each time. I also killed a handfull of them each time. I basically hung out in the bar area and kept it clean with my 51 necro. I had the pet just killing everything in the area. Finally when the heart dropped I logged in my wizzy and looted it.<br>
<br>
Good luck, and hang in there. It's worth it. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ualinestormbringer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aline Stormbringer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 72<br> <font color=#ffffff>(11/13/01 7:25 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Staff of Temperate flux; Heart of Fire</span><hr size=1> Well, seeing this I consider myself lucky.  I ran in there, found an inferno goblin wizard and a room to the right of the bar, Ice Cometed the inferno goblin wizzy in there and got the heart.  In and out in 5 minutes.  If you don't get it on the first spawn, I wouldn't think it would be worth it staying and waiting there.  Just check back every few days and see if anything is up. <p><A <center> <center> <center> <A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=9932"><IMG SRC="http://runnen.homestead.com/files/Alinesig.JPG"></A></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umynameisfizz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>My name is Fizz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br>  Posts: 222<br> <font color=#ffffff>(11/14/01 6:17 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Staff of Temperate flux; Heart of Fire</span><hr size=1> Heart of frost is fun to get, I ran around in all of perma, except IG area, and tried to aggro as many gobbies as possible then I just hade my own AE-group <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--E