<br>
1) go camp an item other than the heart.  You will likely get some loot as well as the heart this way.  Personally my hearts of fire came from an area near sol b and from a cave, neither from the bar.  Heart of frost came from preacher and from a spawn near alchemist in perma.<br>
<br>
2) For sol a get a group.  Helps with the boredom, and also you can pull a bigger area = more kills = better chance of a spawn.<br>
<br>
3) use /auction or /shout and ask for a heart if one drops, most people are nice enough that they will let you loot a no drop item they cant use.  Also, ask for location of inferno wizard spawns if anyone sees them (they might no kill them) <p><hr>
