<br>
I got my off the PH for the bartender, a regular inferno goblin, but it took many hours of camping to get one.<br>
<br>
That suggestion of go hunt other things in the area is a great one as you can get some nice drops off of the mobs from that area.  Just watch out for some of the caster's as they can be nasty business.<br>
<br>
Goroen<br>
